# Configuring Named Mode IPv6

ipv6 unicast-routing
router eigrp CAMPUS_A
  address-family ipv6 unicast autonomous-system 10 #autonomous system doesn't have to be the same as IPv4

# automatically eigrp is turned on and you can disable eigrp by going to af-interface

# seeing neighbors and interfaces

show eigrp address-family ipv6 interface
show eigrp address-family ipv6 neighbor
show eigrp address-family ipv6 topology
